  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Info:</u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Particle is a procedurally generated one-stick idle shooter game where you play as a microscopic robot fending off a bio-mechanical plague. Destroy enemies, pick up items, and survive for as long as possible to achieve a new high score.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Controls:</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press [Enter] to start the game  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hover the [Mouse] to pick up items  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold [Left Mouse Button] to shoot enemies  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press [R] to restart </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press [Escape] to quit game  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press [M] to mute game audio </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press [P] to play game audio  </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Info:</u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Particle is a procedurally generated one-stick idle shooter game where you play as a microscopic robot fending off a bio-mechanical plague. Destroy enemies, pick up items, and survive for as long as possible to achieve a new high score.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Controls:</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press [Enter] to start the game  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hover the [Mouse] to pick up items  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold [Left Mouse Button] to shoot enemies  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press [R] to restart </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press [Escape] to quit game  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press [M] to mute game audio </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press [P] to play game audio  </p>",
